track_notes: I parked my mountain bike near the fountain... you can come by car here, but the small road may be closed, depending on the fire restriction in summer time. If the summit is crowded it will be difficult to setup a dipole! Vertical is much beter in this case.
Nice place to be! Look at the other comments for more info
